            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberto</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Wilielmus">Guglielmo</name></persName> e la
                        moglie <persName><name ref="Matilda">Matilde</name></persName>, figlia di
                                <persName><name ref="Rodelandus">Rodilando</name></persName>, con il
                        consenso del marito, interrogata dal <rs key="#Judge">giudice imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Signorectus">Signoretto</name></persName>,
                        offrono pro anima loro e della defunta <persName><name ref="Alda"
                                >Alda</name></persName>, madre di Lamberto, al <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Confinia #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/603">San Pietro</orgName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/336">Campomaiore</placeName>, omnibus casis et terris et
                        rebus poste in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/2714"
                            >Isula</placeName> et in loco <placeName ref="#places/2714"
                            >Casule</placeName> e tenute da <persName><name ref="Cicius"
                                >Cecio</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Angiorellus"
                                >Angiorello</name></persName> per il censo annuale di 16 denari
                        dâ€™argento; nostram portionem di un appezzamento di terra, quod est campo,
                        posto in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/3122">Tribiano</placeName>,
                            <rs key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">confinante</rs> uno capo con
                        terra di <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Raginmundus"/>Raimondo</persName> et de consorte suo, alio capo
                        con terra del <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">fu <name
                                ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName>, lato uno con terra di
                            <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gherardo</name></persName>, alio lato in via publica. Chiedono al
                            <rs key="#Notary #Writer">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Albertus"
                            >Alberto</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum loco et
                        finibus <placeName ref="#places/3121">Pedone</placeName>. <rs key="#Witness"
                            >Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Crescentius">Crescenzio</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                <name ref="Bonicus">Bonico</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bulgarellus">Bulgarello</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Anselmus">Anselmo</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Genus">Geno</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Morectus">Moretto</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
